# radroots_replica_sync

This is the README for `radroots_replica_sync`, which provides replica ingest
and synchronization interfaces for the `radroots` core libraries.

## Overview

 * typed request, bundle, selector, and transfer-version models for replica
   sync flows;
 * event-emission helpers that materialize replica-facing events from local
   state;
 * ingest helpers, outcomes, and id-factory abstractions for applying incoming
   events;
 * a `std` feature that adds default id generation and higher-level ingest
   entry points.

